t\">\n\t\t\t\t\tagent-ready infrastructure\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t</h1>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"text-xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl\">\n\t\t\t\tAI-innovator suite brings together experimental tasks, evaluation\n\t\t\t\ttooling, and Human-Agent Interfaces to measure an agent's\n\t\t\t\tability to produce novel research-grade insights.\n\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start\">\n\t\t\t\t<a \n\t\t\t\t\thref=\"/docs\" \n\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-purple-400 rounded-full hover:from-blue-300 hover:to-purple-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl\"\n\t\t\t\t>\n\t\t\t\t\tExplore Docs\n\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a \n\t\t\t\t\thref=\"/leaderboard\" \n\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100 bg-slate-800/70 backdrop-blur-sm border border-blue-500/20 rounded-full hover:bg-blue-500/10 hover:border-blue-400/40 transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300\"\n\t\t\t\t>\n\t\t\t\t\tView Leaderboard\n\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<!-- Hero Visual -->\n\t\t<div class=\"relative bg-slate-800/70 backdrop-blur-sm border border-blue-500/20 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-2xl shadow-blue-900/10 min-h-[450px] flex items-end\">\n\t\t\t<!-- Background Gradient -->\n\t\t\t<div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/20 via-transparent to-purple-500/20 rounded-3xl opacity-80\"></div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<!-- Content Grid -->\n\t\t\t<div class=\"relative z-10 w-full grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-sm border border-blue-500/20 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-100 mb-2\">Benchmark</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t20 LLM Research tasks curated from top-tier conferences and latest papers.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-sm border border-orange-500/20 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-100 mb-2\">ResearchGym</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tSandbox your custom agents with Dockerized tools & evaluation loops.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-sm border border-green-500/20 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-100 mb-2\">HAI Console</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tObserve decisions, inject human feedback, and replay trajectories.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-sm border border-purple-500/20 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-100 mb-2\">Evolving Model</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tEvolve the model through human-agent interaction.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</header>\n\n\t<!-- Leaderboard Section -->\n\t<section class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20\" id=\"leaderboard\">\n\t\t<div class=\"text-center mb-16\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-100 mb-6 tracking-tight\">Leaderboard</h2>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\">\n\t\t\t\tA live snapshot of leading agents across all InnovatorBench\n\t\t\t\ttracks. Submit your model via the Registry to appear in the next\n\t\t\t\trefresh.\n\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<LeaderboardChart client:load />\n\n\t</section>\n</Layout>\n"}}}]},{"parts":[{"functionCall":{"id":"toolu_vrtx_019nNc5fNDiXGenKKQcmsXhp","name":"read_file","args":{"absolute_path":"/data2/wuyz/ai-engineer-benchmark-dev-react-agent/web_pages/src/layouts/Layout.astro"}}}],"role":"model"},{"role":"user","parts":[{"functionResponse":{"id":"toolu_vrtx_019nNc5fNDiXGenKKQcmsXhp","name":"read_file","response":{"output":"---\nimport '../styles/global.css'\nimport GAIRLogoPng from \"../images/GAIR_Logo2.png\";\n\n// Get current page path for navigation highlighting\nconst currentPath = Astro.url.pathname;\n\n// Function to check if a nav link should be active\nfunction isActiveLink(href: string): boolean {\n  if (href === '/') {\n    return currentPath === '/';\n  }\n  \n  // Special case for tasks - also highlight when on individual task pages\n  if (href === '/tasks') {\n    return currentPath === '/tasks' || currentPath.startsWith('/task/');\n  }\n  \n  return currentPath.startsWith(href);\n}\n---\n\n<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n\t<head>\n\t\t<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n\t\t<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n\t\t<title>\n\t\t\t{Astro.props.title || \"AI-Innovator · InnovatorBench Benchmark\"}\n\t\t</title>\n\t\t<meta\n\t\t\tname=\"description\"\n\t\t\tcontent={Astro.props.description ||\n\t\t\t\t\"AI-Innovator is the home of InnovatorBench, a benchmark suite for evaluating research-ready AI agents. Explore docs, registry, leaderboard, news, and related papers.\"}\n\t\t/>\n\t\t<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\" />\n\t\t<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin />\n\t\t<link\n\t\t\thref=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap\"\n\t\t\trel=\"stylesheet\"\n\t\t/>\n\t\t<link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/png\" href={GAIRLogoPng.src} />\n\t\t<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href={GAIRLogoPng.src} />\n\t\t\n\t\t<meta name=\"generator\" content={Astro.generator} />\n\t</head>\n\t<body>\n\t\t<nav class=\"nav\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"nav__inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"brand\" href=\"/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<img\n\t\t\t\t\t\tsrc=\"/src/images/GAIR_logo.svg\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\talt=\"GAIR Logo\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"brand__logo\"\n\t\t\t\t\t/>\n\t\t\t\t\t<