nt\">\n\t\t\t\t\tagent-ready infrastructure\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t</h1>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"text-xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl\">\n\t\t\t\tAI-innovator suite brings together experimental tasks, evaluation\n\t\t\t\ttooling, and Human-Agent Interfaces to measure an agent's\n\t\t\t\tability to produce novel research-grade insights.\n\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start\">\n\t\t\t\t<a \n\t\t\t\t\thref=\"/docs\" \n\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-purple-400 rounded-full hover:from-blue-300 hover:to-purple-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl\"\n\t\t\t\t>\n\t\t\t\t\tExplore Docs\n\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a \n\t\t\t\t\thref=\"/leaderboard\" \n\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100 bg-slate-800/70 backdrop-blur-sm border border-blue-500/20 rounded-full hover:bg-blue-500/10 hover:border-blue-400/40 transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300\"\n\t\t\t\t>\n\t\t\t\t\tView Leaderboard\n\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<!-- Hero Visual -->\n\t\t<div class=\"relative bg-slate-800/70 backdrop-blur-sm border border-blue-500/20 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-2xl shadow-blue-900/10 min-h-[450px] flex items-end\">\n\t\t\t<!-- Background Gradient -->\n\t\t\t<div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/20 via-transparent to-purple-500/20 rounded-3xl opacity-80\"></div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<!-- Content Grid -->\n\t\t\t<div class=\"relative z-10 w-full grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-sm border border-blue-500/20 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-100 mb-2\">Benchmark</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t20 LLM Research tasks curated from top-tier conferences and latest papers.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-sm border border-orange-500/20 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-100 mb-2\">ResearchGym</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tSandbox your custom agents with Dockerized tools & evaluation loops.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-sm border border-green-500/20 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-100 mb-2\">HAI Console</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tObserve decisions, inject human feedback, and replay trajectories.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-sm border border-purple-500/20 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-100 mb-2\">Evolving Model</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tEvolve the model through human-agent interaction.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</header>\n\n\t<!-- Leaderboard Section -->\n\t<section class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20\" id=\"leaderboard\">\n\t\t<div class=\"text-center mb-16\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-100 mb-6 tracking-tight\">Leaderboard</h2>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\">\n\t\t\t\tA live snapshot of leading agents across all InnovatorBench\n\t\t\t\ttracks. Submit your model via the Registry to appear in the next\n\t\t\t\trefresh.\n\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<LeaderboardChart client:load />\n\n\t</section>\n</Layout>\n"}}}]},{"parts":[{"functionCall":{"id":"toolu_vrtx_019nNc5fNDiXGenKKQcmsXhp","name":"read_file","args":{"absolute_path":"/data2/wuyz/ai-engineer-benchmark-dev-react-agent/web_pages/src/layouts/Layout.astro"}}}],"role":"model"},{"role":"user","parts":[{"functionResponse":{"id":"toolu_vrtx_019nNc5fNDiXGenKKQcmsXhp","name":"read_file","response":{"output":"---\nimport '../styles/global.css'\nimport GAIRLogoPng from \"../images/GAIR_Logo2.png\";\n\n// Get current page path for navigation highlighting\nconst currentPath = Astro.url.pathname;\n\n// Function to check if a nav link should be active\nfunction isActiveLink(href: string): boolean {\n  if (href === '/') {\n    return currentPath === '/';\n  }\n  \n  // Special case for tasks - also highlight when on individual task pages\n  if (href === '/tasks') {\n    return currentPath === '/tasks' || currentPath.startsWith('/task/');\n  }\n  \n  return currentPath.startsWith(href);\n}\n---\n\n<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n\t<head>\n\t\t<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n\t\t<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n\t\t<title>\n\t\t\t{Astro.props.title || \"AI-Innovator · InnovatorBench Benchmark\"}\n\t\t</title>\n\t\t<meta\n\t\t\tname=\"description\"\n\t\t\tcontent={Astro.props.description ||\n\t\t\t\t\"AI-Innovator is the home of InnovatorBench, a benchmark suite for evaluating research-ready AI agents. Explore docs, registry, leaderboard, news, and related papers.\"}\n\t\t/>\n\t\t<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\" />\n\t\t<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin />\n\t\t<link\n\t\t\thref=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap\"\n\t\t\trel=\"stylesheet\"\n\t\t/>\n\t\t<link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/png\" href={GAIRLogoPng.src} />\n\t\t<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href={GAIRLogoPng.src} />\n\t\t\n\t\t<meta name=\"generator\" content={Astro.generator} />\n\t</head>\n\t<body>\n\t\t<nav class=\"nav\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"nav__inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"brand\" href=\"/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<img\n\t\t\t\t\t\tsrc=\"/src/images/GAIR_logo.svg\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\talt=\"GAIR Logo\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"brand__logo\"\n\t\t\t\t\t/>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"brand__text\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t><strong>AI Innovator Suite</strong></span\n\t\t\t\t\t>\n\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"nav__links\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a class={`nav__link ${isActiveLink('/docs') ? 'nav__link--active' : ''}`} href=\"/docs\">Docs</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a class={`nav__link ${isActiveLink('/tasks') ? 'nav__link--active' : ''}`} href=\"/tasks\">Tasks</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a class={`nav__link ${isActiveLink('/registry') ? 'nav__link--active' : ''}`} href=\"/registry\">Registry</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class={`nav__link ${isActiveLink('/leaderboard') ? 'nav__link--active' : ''}`} href=\"/leaderboard\">Leaderboard</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a class={`nav__link ${isActiveLink('/news') ? 'nav__link--active' : ''}`} href=\"/news\">News</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a class={`nav__link ${isActiveLink('/papers') ? 'nav__link--active' : ''}`} href=\"/papers\">Papers</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</nav>\n\t\t<main>\n\t\t\t<slot />\n\t\t</main>\n\t\t<footer class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 mt-16 border-t border-blue-500/20 text-slate-400\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4\">\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"text-sm\">© 2025 AI Innovator Team · SII-GAIR.</span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"text-sm text-center\">\n\t\t\t\t\tLooking to contribute? Visit the <a href=\"/registry\" class=\"text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors duration-200\">Registry section</a> or open an\n\t\t\t\t\tissue in the GitHub repository.\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</footer>\n\t\t<script src=\"/js/main.js\" is:inline></script>\n\t</body>\n</html>\n\n<style>\n\thtml,\n\tbody {\n\t\tmargin: 0;\n\t\twidth: 100%;\n\t\theight: 100%;\n\t}\n</style>\n"}}}]},{"parts":[{"functionCall":{"id":"toolu_vrtx_01FjuP9bU9P9ZxS6kHBBgY4K","name":"read_file","args":{"absolute_path":"/data2/wuyz/ai-engineer-benchmark-dev-react-agent/web_pages/src/styles/global.css","limit":50}}}],"role":"model"},{"role":"user","parts":[{"functionResponse":{"id":"toolu_vrtx_01FjuP9bU9P9ZxS6kHBBgY4K","name":"read_file","response":{"output":"[File content truncated: showing lines 1-50 of 586 total lines. Use offset/limit parameters to view more.]\n@import \"tailwindcss\";\n\n/* Custom CSS Variables for consistent theming */\n:root {\n  --page-bg: #040810;\n  --surface: rgba(12, 20, 38, 0.7);\n  --surface-strong: rgba(16, 28, 52, 0.85);\n  --glass-border: rgba(120, 178, 255, 0.2);\n  --primary: #66b8ff;\n  --primary-strong: #4da3ff;\n  --secondary: #7b7fff;\n  --accent: #ff8a65;\n  --text-high: #f5f7ff;\n  --text-mid: #c3c9d8;\n  --text-low: #8892b0;\n  --card-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(2, 9, 26, 0.45);\n  --font-sans: \"Inter\", \"Segoe UI\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, sans-serif;\n}\n\n/* Base styles */\n* {\n  box-sizing: border-box;\n}\n\nhtml {\n  scroll-behavior: smooth;\n}\n\nbody {\n  margin: 0;\n  min-height: 100vh;\n  background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(88, 132, 255, 0.32), transparent 55%),\n    radial-gradient(circle at 15% 20%, rgba(255, 138, 101, 0.18), transparent 45%),\n    var(--page-bg);\n  background-attachment: fixed;\n  color: var(--text-high);\n  font-family: var(--font-sans);\n  line-height: 1.6;\n  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n  padding-bottom: 4rem;\n  padding-top: 64px;\n}\n\na {\n  color: inherit;\n  text-decoration: none;\n}\n\n/* Navigation styles - keeping custom nav since it's complex */\n.nav {"}}}]},{"parts":[{"text":"现在我来创建 contributors.astro 页面，遵循项目的设计风格和约定："}],"role":"model"},{"parts":[{"functionCall":{"id":"toolu_vrtx_01CQPcudRLwKj3RjVFxSr9qs","name":"write_file","args":{"file_path":"/data2/wuyz/ai-engineer-benchmark-dev-react-agent/web_pages/src/pages/contributors.astro","content":"---\nimport Layout from \"../layouts/Layout.astro\";\n\nconst title = \"Contributors · AI-Innovator\";\nconst description = \"Meet the contributors who make AI-Innovator possible. Explore the team behind InnovatorBench and acknowledge their contributions.\";\n\n// Sample contributors data - you can replace this with actual data\nconst contributors = [\n\t{\n\t\tname: \"Dr. Alice Chen\",\n\t\trole: \"Lead Researcher\",\n\t\tdescription: \"Specializes in AI agent evaluation and benchmark design. Led the development of InnovatorBench core framework.\",\n\t\tavatar: \"AC\"\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\tname: \"Bob Martinez\",\n\t\trole: \"Software Engineer\",\n\t\tdescription: \"Full-stack developer focused on the ResearchGym infrastructure and HAI Console implementation.\",\n\t\tavatar: \"BM\"\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\tname: \"Dr. Sarah Kim\",\n\t\trole: \"Research Scientist\",\n\t\tdescription: \"Expert in human-AI interaction and evaluation metrics. Designed the human feedback integration system.\",\n\t\tavatar: \"SK\"\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\tname: \"David Thompson\",\n\t\trole: \"DevOps Engineer\",\n\t\tdescription: \"Maintains the benchmark infrastructure and ensures scalable deployment across different environments.\",\n\t\tavatar: \"DT\"\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\tname: \"Dr. Elena Rodriguez\",\n\t\trole: \"AI Ethics Researcher\",\n\t\tdescription: \"Focuses on responsible AI evaluation and bias detection in agent performance assessment.\",\n\t\tavatar: \"ER\"\n\t},\n\t{\n\t\tname: \"Michael Zhang\",\n\t\trole: \"Frontend Developer\",\n\t\tdescription: \"Designed and implemented the user interface for the leaderboard and task visualization components.\",\n\t\tavatar: \"MZ\"\n\t}\n];\n---\n\n<Layout {title} {description}>\n\t<!-- Hero Section -->\n\t<header class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 text-center\">\n\t\t<h1 class=\"text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-100 mb-6 tracking-tight\">\n\t\t\tContributors\n\t\t</h1>\n\t\t<p class=\"text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\">\n\t\t\tMeet the talented individuals who make AI-Innovator possible. \n\t\t\tFrom research to development, each contributor brings unique expertise \n\t\t\tto advance the field of AI agent evaluation.\n\t\t</p>\n\t</header>\n\n\t<!-- Contributors Grid -->\n\t<section class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-12\">\n\t\t<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8\">\n\t\t\t{contributors.map((contributor) => (\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"bg-slate-800/70 backdrop-blur-sm border border-blue-500/20 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-2xl shadow-blue-900/10 hover:border-blue-400/40 hover:bg-slate-800/80 transform hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<!-- Avatar -->\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"flex justify-center mb-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-purple-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-slate-900 font-bold text-xl\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{contributor.avatar}\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<!-- Name and Role -->\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"text-center mb-4\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-100 mb-2\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{contributor.name}\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"text-blue-400 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{contributor.role}\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<!-- Description -->\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed text-center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t{contributor.description}\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t))}\n\t\t</div>\n\t</section>\n\n\t<!-- Acknowledgements Section -->\n\t<section class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20\">\n\t\t<div class=\"bg-slate-800/70 backdrop-blur-sm border border-blue-500/20 rounded-3xl p-12 shadow-2xl shadow-blue-900/10\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"text-center mb-12\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-100 mb-6 tracking-tight\">\n\t\t\t\t\tAcknowledgements\n\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-purple-400 mx-auto rounded-full\"></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-8 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed\">\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"text-lg\">\n\t\t\t\t\tWe extend our heartfelt gratitude to the 